  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK218">
<l>iṭaṉil paruvattu moppuraviṟ kolkār</l>
<l>kaṭaṉaṟi kāṭci yavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The wise who know what is duty will not scant their benevolence even when they are without wealth.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
